  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a captivating world where friendship and personal growth are the true heart of the experience. It all begins when you meet Reiko, a young girl facing her own challenges. Seeing her cry during your first encounter ignites an irresistible urge to help her, setting in motion a connection that will deepen over time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From your first day at the institute, you will have the opportunity to attend classes and hone your skills in various areas. Each day allows you to read books in the library, train at the gym, or explore different locations, from colorful cafés to tranquil green spaces. Every activity is an opportunity to interact and strengthen your relationship with Reiko.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additionally, you will have the chance to get a part-time job that will allow you to earn money and gain new experiences. As you develop your skills and forge bonds, you can also cultivate your own garden thanks to a charming farming system, adding a unique dimension to your school life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While you'll enjoy over 30 exciting mini-games, these are merely a complement to the true essence of the game: forging a special bond with Reiko. Earning tickets through the mini-games will allow you to exchange them for gifts that solidify your friendship, but remember that the most important aspect is the mutual growth you will experience together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to live a unique experience where helping Reiko and building an unbreakable friendship is the true goal. Adventure, growth, and friendship await you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590710/extras/fb1c13ebd5fa7b300709b2ae650a0066.poster.avif?t=1730427860\" width=590 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590710/extras/fb1c13ebd5fa7b300709b2ae650a0066.webm?t=1730427860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590710/extras/fb1c13ebd5fa7b300709b2ae650a0066.mp4?t=1730427860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590710/extras/161dacb0e13c316689a1c85e99c8bedc.poster.avif?t=1730427860\" width=590 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590710/extras/161dacb0e13c316689a1c85e99c8bedc.webm?t=1730427860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590710/extras/161dacb0e13c316689a1c85e99c8bedc.mp4?t=1730427860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590710/extras/948a70256a902108a6d71847cf7033e2.poster.avif?t=1730427860\" width=590 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590710/extras/948a70256a902108a6d71847cf7033e2.webm?t=1730427860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590710/extras/948a70256a902108a6d71847cf7033e2.mp4?t=1730427860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590710/extras/166b94d13acbb020e7a898978f1f2987.poster.avif?t=1730427860\" width=590 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590710/extras/166b94d13acbb020e7a898978f1f2987.webm?t=1730427860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590710/extras/166b94d13acbb020e7a898978f1f2987.mp4?t=1730427860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590710/extras/401f1d949b49203b9fc44da058748da8.poster.avif?t=1730427860\" width=590 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590710/extras/401f1d949b49203b9fc44da058748da8.webm?t=1730427860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2590710/extras/401f1d949b49203b9fc44da058748da8.mp4?t=1730427860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
